               <p>JAMES JOBSON. I am a <rs id="t18260112-74-viclabel420" type="occupation">shoemaker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260112-74-victim478 t18260112-74-viclabel420"></join>. I missed six or seven pairs of boys' boots, which had been tied safe at my door about ten minutes before. The lad came and told me they were taken - I have not seen them since.</p>
